DiamondCorp Says 1,321 Carats Sold at Tender for Average of $94 Per Carat

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-02-24T07:31:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/diamondcorp-says-1-321-carats-sold-at-tender-for-average-of-94-per-carat.html
  DiamondCorp Plc  said 1,312 carats of
gems that were recovered from tailings at its Lace mine were
sold at tender in Johannesburg this week for $94 per carat.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
